snippet.textDisplay: Coke Stodio 🎻 ko ek mashwara dayna chahta hun. Wo ye keh agar playback singers main say kisi ek ko aisa rakha jaye keh wo Marvi jaisay Baray Gulukar ko ganay kay beech hi main ek unchay sur ka alaaaaap day. Or pher dobara song agay barhay. Poori dunya main aisa koi nahin karta. Ye karkay aap ek naee shuruat kar dain gay. Bahot mazedar Song banay ga. Lekin wo Playback Singer koi naya chehra or young chehra hona chahiye 🙏🏼🕊. God bless Coke Stodio God bless Pakistan 🇵🇰. Pakistan Zindabad
